    <body>
        
        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Down</placeName>
                    <date>D 17/80</date>
                    <salute>My dear Prof Allman</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>Will you be so kind as to read over the enclosed memorial, about which I feel the deepest interest.<ref target="#foot.f1"/> If you agree, will you sign it and append “Pres Linnean Soc”. Huxley &amp; I think it best to get only about a dozen signatures and all of men who have done good scientific work.<ref target="#foot.f2"/> Hooker &amp; Lubbock will sign—<ref target="#foot.f3"/> It will save a day’s post if you will place the memorial in the envelope addressed to Prof Flower Pres Zoolg Soc—<ref target="#foot.f4"/></p>
<p>Believe me my dear Prof Allman | Yours very sincerely | Ch Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
        
        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">The enclosure was the memorial to obtain a government pension for <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_4935.xml">Alfred Russel Wallace</ref>. It has not been found, but there is a draft of it in DAR 196: 3; for a transcription, see Appendix VI.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f2">Allman was president of the <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_2944.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Linnean Society</ref>. CD and <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_2486.xml">Thomas Henry Huxley</ref> had discussed the wording of the memorial when CD was in London earlier in the month (see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-12906.xml">letter from T. H. Huxley, 11 December 1880</ref>).</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3"><ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_2357.xml">Joseph Dalton Hooker</ref> and <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_3026.xml">John Lubbock</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f4"><ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1670.xml">William Henry Flower</ref> was president of the <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_5302.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Zoological Society of London</ref>.</note>
        </div>
    
